snippet.title: Channel 4
snippet.description:
Welcome to Channel 4’s YouTube channel - Altogether Different since 1982. Publicly owned, funded by adverts. Champions unheard voices, takes bold creative risks, inspires change and stands up for diversity. Likes chilled rose and long walks on the beach.

Our YouTube channel is jam-packed with clips from much-loved classics like Peep Show and The Great British Bake Off, and brand new hits like We Are Lady Parts and It’s A Sin.
 
Whether you want to investigate the latest Dispatches, laugh your socks off at The Inbetweeners, or snuggle up on the sofa with your favourite Goggleboxers, there’s something for everyone right here.
